1547","1425":"1425","1434":"1434","1478":"1478","1432":"1432","1420":"1420","September 1450":"septembre 1450","1430":"1430","1439":"1439","22 September 1450":"22 septembre 1450","Northampton, Northamptonshire, England":"Northampton, Northamptonshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Northamptonshire, England":"Northamptonshire, Angleterre","Sywell, Northamptonshire, Olde England":"Sywell, Northamptonshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Harrowden, Northamptonshire, England":"Harrowden, Northamptonshire, Angleterre","Wolfage, Northamptonshire, England":"Northamptonshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Lorsque Sir William Tresham est né en 1404, à Northampton, Northamptonshire, Angleterre, son père, Thomas Tresham, avait 44 ans et sa mère, Filia Rempston, avait 44 ans. Il a épousé Lady Isabelle Vaux en 1434, à Northampton, Northamptonshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fils et 2 filles. En 1439, à l’âge de 35 ans, sa profession de son indiquée est speaker of the house of commons. Il est décédé le 22 septembre 1450, à Harrowden, Northamptonshire, Angleterre, à l’âge de 46 ans, et a été enterré à Harrowden, Northamptonshire, Angleterre."},"de":{"1404–22 September 1450":"1404–22. September 1450","1404–1450":"1404–1450","1404–1478":"1404–1478","1420–1471":"1420–1471","1425–Female":"1425–Verstorben","1450–1547":"1450–1547","1360–Male":"1360–Verstorben","1360–Female":"1360–Verstorben","1450":"1450","1471":"1471","1360":"1360","1404":"1404","1547":"1547","1425":"1425","1434":"1434","1478":"1478","1432":"1432","1420":"1420","September 1450":"September 1450","1430":"1430","1439":"1439","22 September 1450":"22. September 1450","Northampton, Northamptonshire, England":"Northampton, Northamptonshire, England, United Kingdom","Northamptonshire, England":"Northamptonshire, England","Sywell, Northamptonshire, Olde England":"Sywell, Northamptonshire, England, United Kingdom","Harrowden, Northamptonshire, England":"Harrowden, Northamptonshire, England","Wolfage, Northam